Googling suggested problem with new setuptools. Downgrading setuptools to version 19 fixes it

sudo rm -R /Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/setuptools*
sudo pip install setuptools==19.2 
bazel test -c opt //tensorflow/python:graph_util_test --test_output=streamed

body:
Googling suggested problem with new setuptools. Downgrading setuptools to version 19 fixes it

```
sudo rm -R /Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/setuptools*
sudo pip install setuptools==19.2 
bazel test -c opt //tensorflow/python:graph_util_test --test_output=streamed
```
